89
00:03:51,959 --> 00:03:53,125
- ALMOST?

90
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:05,917
- GET OUT OF HERE.

91
00:04:05,959 --> 00:04:08,291
WE DON'T HAVE ANYTHING LEFT.

92
00:04:18,458 --> 00:04:20,875
- NOW, YOU DON'T
HAVE ANYTHING LEFT.

93
00:04:26,542 --> 00:04:30,208
[bison grumbles]

94
00:04:31,458 --> 00:04:32,625
[all gasp]

95
00:04:47,083 --> 00:04:49,500
[all scream]

96
00:04:54,583 --> 00:04:56,250
- IT'S SAFE TO
COME OUT EVERYONE,

97
00:04:56,291 --> 00:04:57,583
THE AIRBENDERS ARE HERE.

98
00:04:57,625 --> 00:05:00,166
- YOU FINALLY MADE IT.

99
00:05:00,208 --> 00:05:02,542
SO, WHERE ARE
THE REST OF YOU?

100
00:05:02,583 --> 00:05:04,750
- ACTUALLY, IT'S JUST
THE TWO OF US,

101
00:05:04,792 --> 00:05:07,375
BUT WE'RE GOING TO DO
EVERYTHING WE CAN TO HELP.

102
00:05:07,417 --> 00:05:09,333
I'M OPAL, AND THIS IS KAI

103
00:05:09,375 --> 00:05:11,166
- IT'S NICE TO MEET YOU.
- WHAT?

104
00:05:11,208 --> 00:05:13,250
I CALLED MASTER TENZIN
BECAUSE MY STATE HAS BEEN

105
00:05:13,291 --> 00:05:15,542
UNDER SIEGE BY BANDITS
FOR MONTHS.

106
00:05:15,583 --> 00:05:19,291
THEY BLOCKED ALL THE ROADS,
CUT OFF OUR SUPPLY LINES,

107
00:05:19,333 --> 00:05:22,750
