112
00:05:29,834 --> 00:05:32,792
OUR ENTIRE STATE
IS ON THE BRINK OF COLLAPSE.

113
00:05:32,834 --> 00:05:34,625
- UNFORTUNATELY,
THE AIR NATION IS

114
