UNTIL THE EARTH KINGDOM

124
00:06:12,417 --> 00:06:14,542
IS 100% REUNITED.

125
00:06:18,166 --> 00:06:19,667
[all scream]

126
00:06:25,667 --> 00:06:27,625
- WHY HAVE WE STOPPED?

127
