THE BANDITS MYSELF.

132
00:07:13,125 --> 00:07:15,208
- GAH!
- O-WAH!

133
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:21,166
- AAH!
- OWW!

134
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:24,500
- AHH!
- ARGH!

135
00:07:24,542 --> 00:07:26,166
- UGH, OOH!

136
00:07:33,667 --> 00:07:35,542
- EHH!
- ACK, OHH!

137
00:07:38,041 --> 00:07:40,041
[all grunting]

138
00:07:48,625 --> 00:07:51,041
[all groaning]

139
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:06,291
- YOU'RE...KUVIRA.

140
00:08:06,333 --> 00:08:08,625
- AND YOU'RE THE BANDITS
WHO HAVE BEEN CAUSING CHAOS

141
00:08:08,667 --> 00:08:11,417
WHERE I AM TRYING TO ESTABLISH
ORDER, AREN'T YOU?

142
00:08:11,458 --> 00:08:12,959
- WE'RE SORRY.

143
