A HAIRCUT.

166
00:09:09,166 --> 00:09:11,583
THE DINNER AT AIR TEMPLE ISLAND
ISN'T UNTIL LATER TONIGHT.

167
00:09:11,625 --> 00:09:12,917
- BECAUSE I'M NOT
JUST GETTING A HAIRCUT.

168
00:09:12,959 --> 00:09:14,375
IT'S A SPA DAY.

169
00:09:14,417 --> 00:09:16,542
WE'RE TALKING
MINIMUM FOUR HOURS.

170
00:09:16,583 --> 00:09:18,083
- ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

171
00:09:18,125 --> 00:09:20,500
