THAT TAKES FOUR HOURS?

172
00:09:20,542 --> 00:09:23,333
- A REJUVENATING
TEA LEAF SKIN WRAP.

173
00:09:23,375 --> 00:09:25,166
HAVE YOU EVER
GOTTEN ONE OF THOSE, MAKO?

174
00:09:25,208 --> 00:09:27,709
[elevator dings]
- YEAH, I'M NOT INTERESTED.

175
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,959
- OH, YOU WILL BE.

176
00:09:31,834 --> 00:09:33,208
[elevator dings]

177
00:09:33,250 --> 00:09:35,250
SO WHILE YOUR HANDS SOAK
IN A BUBBLING MILK BATH,

178
00:09:35,291 --> 00:09:37,792
YOUR FEET ARE IN A TUB
FULL OF THESE LITTLE SUCKERFISH

179
00:09:37,834 --> 00:09:39,583
THAT LITERALLY EAT
YOUR CALLUSES AWAY.

180
00:09:39,625 --> 00:09:42,291
GOBBLE THEM RIGHT UP.
CRAZY, HUH?

181
00:09:42,333 --> 00:09:43,875
- THAT'S DISGUSTING.

182
00:09:43,917 --> 00:09:46,667
- THEN THEY SCRAPE YOUR SKIN
WITH BLOCKS OF SEA SALT,

183
00:09:46,709 --> 00:09:48,917
LUBE YOU UP WITH
SEAWEED INFUSED ALOE,

184
00:09:48,959 --> 00:09:50,625
WRAP YOU IN TEA LEAVES,
PUT YOU IN A HOT BOX

185
00:09:50,667 --> 00:09:53,291
FOR FOUR HOURS AND BAM,
YOU'RE DONE!

186
00:09:53,333 --> 00:09:54,875
[cheers and boos
from the crowd]

187
00:09:54,917 --> 00:09:57,125
MAKO, LOOK AT ALL MY FANS.

188
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:59,500
THEY MUST BE IN TOWN
FOR MY CORONATION.

189
00:09:59,542 --> 00:10:04,000
- UH, I DON'T KNOW IF ALL
THOSE PEOPLE ARE YOUR FANS.

190
00:10:04,041 --> 00:10:07,583
men: BOO!

191
00:10:07,625 --> 00:10:09,166
- YEAH!

192
00:10:09,208 --> 00:10:14,750
ALL RIGHT, WU!
[whooping]

193
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:27,166
- WU, WE HAVE TO GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.

194
00:10:27,208 --> 00:10:29,875
- WHAT?

195
00:10:33,208 --> 00:10:36,709
- GO, GO.

196
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,375
- WHAT JUST HAPPENED OUT THERE?

197
00:10:38,417 --> 00:10:41,625
- I THINK THOSE WERE KUVIRA
SUPPORTERS IN THE CROWD.

198
00:10:41,667 --> 00:10:43,583
- OH, NO!
MAKO, I'VE BEEN HIT.

199
00:10:43,625 --> 00:10:45,250
IT'S A GUSHER.

200
