- THAT'S NOT BLOOD,
IT'S STRAWBERRY PIE.

201
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:50,291
- HMM.

202
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:53,709
OH, YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
BUT THAT WAS CLOSE.

203
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:55,750
I DON'T KNOW WHAT WOULD'VE
HAPPENED IF YOU WEREN'T THERE.

204
00:10:55,792 --> 00:10:57,834
- YOU WOULD'VE BEEN HIT
BY A PIE.

205
00:10:57,875 --> 00:10:59,417
IT'S REALLY NOT
THAT BIG OF A DEAL.

206
00:10:59,458 --> 00:11:00,834
- OR I COULD'VE BEEN KILLED.

207
00:11:00,875 --> 00:11:03,458
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I'D EVER
DO WITHOUT YOU.

208
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:06,542
WAIT A SECOND,
DID YOU SAY STRAWBERRY PIE?

209
00:11:06,583 --> 00:11:09,250
I'M ALLERGIC TO STRAWBERRIES.

210
00:11:09,291 --> 00:11:10,917
I DON'T THINK I CAN BREATHE.

211
00:11:10,959 --> 00:11:13,208
GET ME TO THE HOSPITAL,
WU DOWN.

212
00:11:13,250 --> 00:11:15,625
- YOU'RE ALLERGIC
TO BEE STINGS.

213
00:11:15,667 --> 00:11:17,000
- OH, RIGHT.

214
00:11:17,041 --> 00:11:18,542
I ALWAYS
GET THOSE TWO MIXED UP.

215
00:11:18,583 --> 00:11:20,709
[whistle blows]

216
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:22,500
- LOOK!
A TRAIN MADE IT THROUGH.

217
00:11:22,542 --> 00:11:24,875
- MAYBE THEY BROUGHT
FOOD AND SUPPLIES.

218
00:11:24,917 --> 00:11:26,834
[hydraulics hiss]

219
00:11:32,875 --> 00:11:35,208
- HEY, WHAT'S YOUR BOYFRIEND
DOING HERE?

220
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:37,667
- IF HE'S HERE, HE MUST BE
WITH KUVIRA AND MY BROTHER.

221
00:11:37,709 --> 00:11:39,500
THIS ISN'T GOING TO BE GOOD.

222
00:11:39,542 --> 00:11:42,291
- BOLIN!
- KAI!

223
00:11:42,333 --> 00:11:43,875
[laughs]

224
00:11:43,917 --> 00:11:46,709
WOW, YOU ARE A LOT HEAVIER
THAN YOU USED TO BE,

225
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,041
YOU'RE REALLY GROWING UP.

226
00:11:48,083 --> 00:11:49,250
- WHAT'S UP WITH YOUR NEW HAIR?

227
00:11:49,291 --> 00:11:50,709
